cause.EN-US: Austin Energy: Maintenance scheduled today in your area may require an interruption in electric service. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.

cause.EN-US: An obstruction to the electrical grid has occurred (e.g., a traffic collision). Restoration time depends on the extent of the damage.
